No, bunnies are not my strongest suit. 🙆‍♀️

node.text:
Heyyy! I’m so excited to share with you guys my collab with @minigallerybox ! 🌈✨ 

There’re three different subscriptions you can find on minigallerybox.com with exclusive goodies such as prints, stickers and a little zine! These will be available until October 1st, link is in my bio if you’d like to know more ☺️ 

I loved working on these designs and I hope you will like them too! Thank you @minigallerybox for this opportunity! ❤️
.
.
.
#minigallerybox

node.text:
I got some witchy stickers from the super cool folks at @stickerapp 🤩❤️ thank you guys! These are huuuggge and such nice quality as always!! There’re two other designs I cannot show yet but they turned out as pretty as these 💕 

I don’t manage myself a shop so these aren’t for sale unfortunately, sorry! BUT I’ll be giving away a bunch of stickers soonnnnnn when we reach 600k!! Maybe sooner because I’m impatient 😂 please stay tuned for that! 

Love y’all, thanks for your support! ✨
.
.
.
#stickers #stickerapp #witch #witchyvibes #digitalart #halloween #witchseason #spooky #stickerappinspo
